    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
      "name": "Distracted by Beauty",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>With a successful @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Perform]{Perform} check against the Red Reaver's Will DC, a character can attempt to fascinate a red reaver within 60 feet who is able to observe the performance (via sight or hearing, whichever is appropriate). Once it gains the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fascinated]{Fascinated} condition, the Red Reaver remains so until the performance stops, it takes damage, or it observes anyone damaging or stealing any of its treasures.</p>"
        },
