      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
      "name": "Roar",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The Red Reaver lets out a loud and horrifying roar. Other creatures within 100 feet must succeed at a @Check[type:will|dc:30] save or become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2} (@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 3} on a critical failure, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1} on a success, or unaffected on a critical success). No matter the result, the creature is temporarily immune to the effect for 1 minute.</p>"
        },
